{"tid":2495001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"情境題： 以下邊一個人有機會犯法 - 煽惑他人選舉投白票","createTime":"2021-04-19T02:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T03:28:37.000Z","uid":187232,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f51ed1882c82cfd9d1d1bce031e3093c69f5113","tid":2495001,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">情境題：<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">以下邊一個人有機會犯法 - 煽惑他人選舉投白票</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個普通市民喺電視機前公開陳述「香港公民投白票不犯法」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特首林鄭月娥喺電視機前公開陳述「香港公民投白票不犯法」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">林鄭月娥被問到當年在特首選舉時，亦有選委在選票中寫上粗口字句，將來是否有關行為亦會被規管，<span class=\"red\">她說，《基本法》保障了香港居民的選舉及被選舉權，而3.11人大常委決定的其中一個原則考慮，就是尊重香港居民選舉及被選舉權，「要有得揀」，強調選票作出哪種展示屬其自由，政府不會規管當日投票選擇，如不投任何候選人或破壞選票致無效。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/3T652GSXNBGLHLY26LMXDP6MN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2F3T652GSXNBGLHLY26LMXDP6MN4%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=725f0903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2F3T652GSXNBGLHLY26LMXDP6MN4%2F&h=720db698\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/3T652GSXNBGLHLY26LMXDP6MN4/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通市民 - 請正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特首林鄭月娥 - 負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e9e21788af84fe174bd3cee5670b7d98a57423","tid":2495001,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"咁我作為一個普通市民<br />\n公開複述特首嘅公開言論犯唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><br />\n特首林鄭月娥說，《基本法》保障了香港居民的選舉及被選舉權，而3.11人大常委決定的其中一個原則考慮，就是尊重香港居民選舉及被選舉權，「要有得揀」，強調選票作出哪種展示屬其自由，政府不會規管當日投票選擇，如不投任何候選人或破壞選票致無效。</span>"},{"pid":"271e721b7b935a2512c415299a75fdc698bfa548","tid":2495001,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:45:01.000Z","msg":"媽我好亂啊～<br />\n特首講「投白票唔犯法」就得<br />\n市民講「投白票唔犯法」就要坐三年<br />\n<br />\n只准州官放火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不准百姓點燈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e72ba836cec86125db4e4880b8a1a3aac700ffd","tid":2495001,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"我知今時今日同政府講邏輯好白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但個邏輯有實例，特首有公開強調過，係基本法保障底下香港市民投白票問題屬原則性問題，政府不會規管投票選擇<br />\n<br />\n咁如果香港市原話覆述特首言論，點解有機會犯法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0eda90f84030ed542fd4e72ee67f9c48379af7","tid":2495001,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acaa8b166d55a81a8a05c67de9d726ec1de8712c","tid":2495001,"uid":360907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:24:32.000Z","msg":"正解：黃絲講「白票」2字已經犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc25d4ec44e817c4156fdfc44fed4c0bb383f45","tid":2495001,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acaa8b166d55a81a8a05c67de9d726ec1de8712c","tid":2495001,"uid":360907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:24:32.000Z","msg":"正解：黃絲講「白票」2字已經犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"Sad but true..."}],"pinned":{"pid":"6e72ba836cec86125db4e4880b8a1a3aac700ffd","tid":2495001,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"我知今時今日同政府講邏輯好白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但個邏輯有實例，特首有公開強調過，係基本法保障底下香港市民投白票問題屬原則性問題，政府不會規管投票選擇<br />\n<br />\n咁如果香港市原話覆述特首言論，點解有機會犯法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}